{"tid":2454932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"12港人話捉就捉到，走私船就點都追唔到","createTime":"2021-03-20T15:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T16:32:42.000Z","uid":105567,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"93c9a210fa795ef38796545b959032bf84563061","tid":2454932,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T15:42:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210320/7EYMYEEJUZGOXNOVNDXGGOQRBM/?fbclid=IwAR3AuWzO64Qw2No-4JWyHH1mjT2lJYn5JszJSoFiWSNQ0HfWMg4rp6vzBMg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210320%2F7EYMYEEJUZGOXNOVNDXGGOQRBM%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3AuWzO64Qw2No-4JWyHH1mjT2lJYn5JszJSoFiWSNQ0HfWMg4rp6vzBMg&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDLTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=c2a95fe4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210320%2F7EYMYEEJUZGOXNOVNDXGGOQRBM%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3AuWzO64Qw2No-4JWyHH1mjT2lJYn5JszJSoFiWSNQ0HfWMg4rp6vzBMg&h=0a3f2a0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210320/7EYMYEEJUZGOXNOVNDXGGOQRBM/?fbclid=IwAR3AuWzO64Qw2No-4JWyHH1mjT2lJYn5JszJSoFiWSNQ0HfWMg4rp6vzBMg</a><br />\n<br />\n疫情下港中兩地通關受阻，令近期屯門一帶海上走私日益猖獗。今日流傳一段短片，可見一艘疑似水警快艇，在屯門青山發電廠對開海域，高速追截一艘疑似走私船，其間水警一度向走私船平射信號彈試圖截停，場面驚心動魄。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳兩段相信由漁民拍攝的片段，可見兩艘快艇在屯門青山發電廠對開海域高速追截，現場雖不見日光但視野尚算清晰，估計時清晨或黃昏時間，然而確實時間不明。<br />\n<br />\n第一段全長約30秒，片段中水警快艇高速追截疑似走私船，旁觀漁民相隔一段距離觀望，不時直言「搏緊命啊」、「撞佢啊嘛」、「截到佢冇油為止」，甚是肉緊。追截一段距離後，走私船急速煞停轉彎，試圖擺脫水警快艇，但水警快艇及時追上，更向走私船發射一枚信號彈，引得圍觀漁民大呼「精采！着火啱呀」。<br />\n<br />\n第二段片段則全長44秒，過程與第一段差不多，可見水警快艇曾先後發射兩枚信號彈，而且貼近走私船，然而走私船不為所動繼續高速逃離，圍觀漁民議論紛紛，更有人向水警大喊開槍，「你唔開槍佢唔停㗎」。然而直至片段結束，依然不知走私船是否已經落網。"},{"pid":"00a7e51b926a674c5abd52043e194c644ea06d58","tid":2454932,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T16:30:32.000Z","msg":"你竟然將小香港水警同偉大社會主義祖國公安相提並論？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69be0fbe41983afffda65eab2866d7f599f57b6c","tid":2454932,"uid":387391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T16:32:42.000Z","msg":"捉手足一定快狠準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}